{"nodes": [{"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_constitution", "label": "Write.OnMars Constitution v1.1.0", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_i_voz_natural", "label": "Principio I: Voz natural y sobria", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "La voz es el principio fundacional; si el texto suena a IA, eslogan o academicismo burocr\u00e1tico, ning\u00fan otro principio salva la gu\u00eda."}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_ii_estructura", "label": "Principio II: situaci\u00f3n \u2192 explicaci\u00f3n \u2192 consecuencia pr\u00e1ctica", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Una gu\u00eda \u00fatil responde de forma constante a '\u00bfqu\u00e9 hago con esto?'; si la secci\u00f3n no produce acci\u00f3n, advertencia o decisi\u00f3n, no pertenece a la gu\u00eda."}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_iii_brief", "label": "Principio III: Brief obligatorio antes de redactar", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Sin brief, humanos y modelos generan texto gen\u00e9rico; el brief es la traducci\u00f3n editorial del Constitution Check de Spec Kit."}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_iv_precision_lexica", "label": "Principio IV: Precisi\u00f3n l\u00e9xica y arquitectura sint\u00e1ctica integrada", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "La autoridad profesional depende de la coherencia entre forma y significado; adopta el rigor de Cabr\u00e9/RAE/Fund\u00e9u/AENOR y el estilo integrado ciceroniano."}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_v_revision_multipasada", "label": "Principio V: Revisi\u00f3n multi-pasada antes de publicar", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Cinco pasadas con preguntas distintas (estructura, utilidad, naturalidad, precisi\u00f3n, formato) evitan que defectos de un dominio contaminen la evaluaci\u00f3n de otro."}, {"id": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_arquitectura_framework", "label": "Arquitectura del framework (skills + MCP + plugins, agnosticismo de agente)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_iv_precision_lexica", "target": "resources_manual_maestro_para_la_produccion_de_textos_especializados_estrategias_de_lexico_cohesion_y_arquitectura_sintactica_terminologia_cabre", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "releases_v1_0_0_constitution_v1_1_0_principio_iv_precision_lexica", "target": "resources_manual_maestro_para_la_produccion_de_textos_especializados_estrategias_de_lexico_cohesion_y_arquitectura_sintactica_estilo_integrado_ciceroniano", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "releases/v1.0.0/constitution-v1.1.0